{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2090795, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 406887, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不是，严格地讲消炎药有甾体的（激素）和非甾体的（大部分退烧药，比如熟知的对乙酰氨基酚）", "timestamp": 1626603993, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2090803, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406887, "reply_to": 2090795, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 诶那普通感冒应该吃什么呀，我之前一直乱吃阿奇霉素肯定不好", "timestamp": 1626604096, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2090829, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406887, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "普通感冒不就对乙酰氨基酚吗 复方感冒药就是对乙酰氨基酚+氯苯那敏", "timestamp": 1626604279, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2090832, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 406887, "reply_to": 2090829, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 对乙酰氨基酚不是退烧药吗hhh", "timestamp": 1626604324, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2090834, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406887, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "阿莫西林 阿奇霉素都是抗生素 切勿滥用 一般来说需要确认是细菌性感冒才有必要服用", "timestamp": 1626604324, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2090837, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406887, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "病毒感染一般不用药，因为像利巴韦林这种抗病毒药物副作用都不小", "timestamp": 1626604391, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2090845, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 406887, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "综上述，普通感冒就用一些复方感冒药就好，包含解热镇痛药（扑热息痛/阿司匹林/布洛芬），抗过敏药（氯苯那敏/氯雷他定），血管舒张药物（麻黄碱/伪麻黄碱）", "timestamp": 1626604506, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2090861, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 406887, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这是两类东西吧", "timestamp": 1626604731, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 406887, "reply": 8, "tag": null, "text": "求问医学问题\n抗生素和消炎药是一个东西吗，还是说是包含关系？\n像一般的普通感冒是病毒感染，对抗细菌的抗生素无效，那么可以吃消炎药吗？能否举例一下\n（突然发现自己也在抗生素滥用orz）", "timestamp": 1626603804, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626604730, "url": "", "vote": {}}}